          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Adjunct Faculty Loan Fairness Act of 2015</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to allow part-time teachers to participate in the William D. Ford Federal Direct Loan forgiveness program for public service employees, if they: (1) teach at least one course at an institution of higher education, a postsecondary vocational institution, or a Tribal College or University; and (2) do not have another full-time job. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-10-05T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
